---
// Pricing.astro
---
<section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-primary border-t border-quaternary">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-theme-white sm:text-4xl mb-4">Inversión transparente para escalar tu negocio</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-secondary">Una solución que pagará por sí sola en la primera semana evitando fricción de cierre de ventas.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Launch Plan -->
      <div class="bg-quaternary/30 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-quaternary flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-theme-white mb-2">Launch</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm mb-6">Para desarrollos pequeños o primera fase.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-theme-white mb-2">$2,200 <span class="text-base font-normal text-secondary">/mes MXN</span></div>
        <div class="text-sm text-secondary mb-8">+ $22,000 setup único</div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Hasta 60 unidades</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Galería, Brochure, video</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Mapa de disponiblidad interactivo</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Cotizador dinámico básico</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Generación de PDFs</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Panel de administración</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Gestión de propiedades</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> 1 lista de precios activa</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> 3 Esquemas de pago</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Hosting Inlcuído</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Soporte estandar</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center py-3 bg-quaternary hover:bg-tertiary hover:text-primary text-theme-white rounded-lg transition font-medium">Comenzar Launch</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Growth Plan -->
      <div class="bg-linear-to-b from-quaternary to-primary rounded-3xl p-1 relative border-2 border-theme-white shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] flex flex-col transform md:-translate-y-4">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-theme-white text-primary font-bold px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">
          Más popular
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary rounded-[22px] p-8 flex flex-col h-full m-0.5">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-theme-white mb-2">Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm mb-6">Para la mayoría de los desarrollos verticales.</p>
          <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-theme-white mb-2">$3,400<span class="text-base font-normal text-secondary">/mes MXN</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm text-secondary mb-8">+ $29,000 setup único</div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Plan Launch Incluído +</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Hasta 150 unidades</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Tour virtual integrado</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Tipologías arquitectónicas detalladas</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Esquemas de pagos múltiples</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Historial de listas de precios</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Actualización por lotes  de precios vía Excel</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> Gestión básica de clientes leads</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-theme-white"><span class="text-tertiary font-bold">✓</span> 10 Listas activasa</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center py-4 bg-theme-white hover:bg-tertiary text-primary rounded-lg transition font-bold shadow-lg">Agendar Demo</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scale Plan -->
      <div class="bg-quaternary/30 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-quaternary flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-theme-white mb-2">Scale</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm mb-6">Master plans, macro lotes o agencias completas.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-theme-white mb-2">Custom</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-secondary mb-8">Setup a la medida</div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Todo el plan Growth +</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Unidades Ilimitadas</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Multiples listas activas</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Personalización Visual Avanzada</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Soporte prioritario</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-tertiary"><span class="text-theme-white">✓</span> Asesoría de optimización comercial</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center py-3 bg-quaternary hover:bg-tertiary hover:text-primary text-theme-white rounded-lg transition font-medium">Contactar ventas</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
